<i> A guy needs to</i>
<i> protect himself,</i>

00:08.242 --> 00:11.076
<i> and your name was</i>
<i> a glorious place to start.</i>

00:11.145 --> 00:12.878
<i> The next thing our little</i>
<i> friend the internet gave me</i>

00:12.947 --> 00:14.446
<i> was your address.</i>

