Oh, you make me insane.

00:25.259 --> 00:27.426
<i> - Oh, Beck, who is this?</i>

00:27.528 --> 00:29.561
<i> Benjamin J. Ashby.</i>
<i> Greenwich born,</i>

00:29.663 --> 00:30.662
<i> boarding school bred.</i>

00:30.731 --> 00:32.464
After you.
