00:32.566 --> 00:34.333
Man, I'm thinkin' maybe--

00:35.936 --> 00:37.236
Do not tell me
that you're doing this

00:37.338 --> 00:38.837
because of Beck!

00:38.906 --> 00:40.706
- I'm very scared
of what you would do to her.

00:40.775 --> 00:43.175
- She show you her ladle? She's
got this red kitchen ladle.

00:43.244 --> 00:45.411
It's a whole "call you Daddy,
spank me" thing.

00:45.513 --> 00:47.346
- Benji, I'd love your help.

00:47.448 --> 00:50.349
<i> Unfortunately, I know</i>
<i> you're a pathological liar.</i>

00:50.451 --> 00:52.317
- [gasps, wheezes]

00:52.420 --> 00:55.354
<i> - I just knew Benji</i>
<i> was the worst kind of poison,</i>

00:55.456 --> 00:57.723
