02:28.883 --> 02:31.750
<i> [light music]</i>

02:31.852 --> 02:36.088
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

02:36.190 --> 02:38.390
<i> - I want to come in, I do.</i>

02:38.492 --> 02:40.425
<i> But I'm gonna make us wait.</i>

02:40.494 --> 02:42.027
<i> You're worth waiting for.</i>
<i> Besides...</i>

02:42.129 --> 02:43.662
