03:20.234 --> 03:22.668
<i> You're dead to me, Benji.</i>
<i> Dead.</i>

03:24.104 --> 03:25.671
<i> Joe: You're finally moving on.</i>

03:25.739 --> 03:27.506
<i> And now that you've</i>
<i> dealt with Benji,</i>

03:27.608 --> 03:30.842
<i> it's time for me</i>
<i> to do the same.</i>

03:30.945 --> 03:33.779
<i> [dark music swells]</i>

