<i> without creating a pretty</i>
<i> damning evidence trail.</i>

03:50.464 --> 03:52.998
<i> So I turn to those</i>
<i> I trust most for tips--</i>

03:53.067 --> 03:56.268
<i> King, Carr, Franzen, Flynn.</i>

03:56.337 --> 03:58.136
<i> Fun fact:</i>
<i> spatchcocking a chicken</i>

03:58.205 --> 03:59.605
<i> and dismembering a human</i>

03:59.707 --> 04:02.074
<i> involve the same six</i>
<i> essential steps.</i>

04:02.176 --> 04:03.976
<i> Not sure I'm down for that.</i>

04:04.078 --> 04:05.811
<i> Little intense.</i>
<i> But...</i>

04:05.879 --> 04:08.213
<i> I think I finally have</i>
<i> a plan for Benji.</i>

04:09.483 --> 04:11.283
- Oh, hey, Joe, I didn't know
you were up there.

04:11.352 --> 04:13.719
Do you mind if I play
some, uh, Enrique Iglesias?

04:13.787 --> 04:15.387
I'm trying to
bone up on my Spanish.

04:15.489 --> 04:16.989
<i> - These are officially</i>
<i> the darkest days...</i>

04:17.091 --> 04:18.657
Sounds great.
<i> In the history of the world.</i>

04:18.726 --> 04:19.825
- I mean, I can pick
something else.

04:19.927 --> 04:21.360
I got a ton of playlists
on here.

04:21.428 --> 04:24.329
I got rock music,
club music, jazz music.

04:24.398 --> 04:26.365
<i> - I wonder if he's a virgin.</i>
Stick with the Iglesias.

04:26.433 --> 04:28.066
I'm just gonna be in the
basement working on some books.

04:28.168 --> 04:29.334
