Professor Mott?

05:49.016 --> 05:50.148
- Beck, is it?

05:50.250 --> 05:52.017
- Yes, hi.
- Blythe.

05:52.086 --> 05:54.019
- [gasps]
- I heard you were joining us.

05:54.121 --> 05:55.687
- Yeah.
- We meet here for workshop

05:55.789 --> 05:57.356
on Tuesdays and Thursdays.

05:57.424 --> 05:59.925
