so bring your A game.

05:59.993 --> 06:01.560
- I intend to.

06:01.662 --> 06:03.995
You know, I actually--
I read one of your essays

06:04.098 --> 06:05.831
in the "Review" last month,

06:05.933 --> 06:08.600
and it was so illuminating.
I tweeted it.

06:08.702 --> 06:12.371
- Social Media. It's like
the next great genocide.

06:14.675 --> 06:16.508
Jersey, right?
- Sorry?

06:16.610 --> 06:18.110
- It's where you're from?

06:18.178 --> 06:20.812
- No, I'm, uh,
