it's my grandparents.

06:53.147 --> 06:54.546
I'll see you
in class, okay?

06:54.648 --> 06:56.047
- Okay.
- Okay.

06:56.150 --> 06:58.417
Hey...
[laughs]

06:58.519 --> 06:59.818
Yeah.

06:59.920 --> 07:01.386
<i> - And then she walked away,</i>

07:01.488 --> 07:03.121
<i> and I melted into the earth.</i>

