08:09.590 --> 08:11.156
You know?
- Wow!

08:11.258 --> 08:13.592
- Joe is still a maybe.

08:13.694 --> 08:16.127
<i> - A maybe?</i>
<i> I'm a</i> maybe?

08:16.230 --> 08:17.729
<i> And you're still screwing</i>
<i> other guys?</i>

08:17.831 --> 08:19.397
<i> Beck!</i>
<i> How did I miss this?</i>

08:19.466 --> 08:22.000
<i> How did I read this</i>
<i> so completely wrong?</i>

08:22.069 --> 08:24.236
- Look, if you wanna bone
Benji outta your system,

08:24.304 --> 08:26.037
more power to you.

08:26.139 --> 08:28.673
