you're respecting yourself.

08:28.775 --> 08:32.077
Look, I'm just saying...

08:32.145 --> 08:35.313
are you being your most
amazing self right now?

08:35.415 --> 08:37.949
- I mean, this is...
this is my process.

08:38.051 --> 08:40.352
It's like a Benji exorcism.

08:40.454 --> 08:43.622
I'm just exploring
my options in a city of...

08:43.724 --> 08:45.524
8 million people.

08:45.626 --> 08:47.292
