- Yeah.

08:47.361 --> 08:48.593
- I'm gonna get a drink.

08:48.695 --> 08:52.631
<i> [pop music in background]</i>

08:52.733 --> 08:54.032
- I like your tattoo.

08:55.335 --> 08:57.168
- I don't have a tattoo.

08:57.237 --> 08:59.204
<i> - Love is patient and kind.</i>
[Beck moaning]

08:59.306 --> 09:00.872
<i> And so am I, Beck.</i>

09:00.974 --> 09:03.174
<i> For you, I can be patient.</i>

09:03.277 --> 09:05.010
<i> Maybe this is your process.</i>

09:05.078 --> 09:06.845
<i> Nobody buys the first pair</i>
<i> of jeans they try on,</i>

09:06.947 --> 09:08.747
<i> no matter how perfect.</i>

09:08.849 --> 09:11.583
<i> But as much as I'm hoping</i>
<i> this is just a stage,</i>

09:11.685 --> 09:13.518
<i> a quick password search</i>
<i> on your iCloud</i>

09:13.620 --> 09:16.187
<i> has revealed a swipe-fest</i>
<i> of millennial man-boys.</i>

09:16.290 --> 09:17.756
<i> Guy with tiger.</i>

09:17.824 --> 09:19.457
<i> Junior William Morris agent.</i>

09:19.560 --> 09:21.826
<i> Viking Wannabe.</i>
<i> You've been a busy girl, Beck.</i>

09:21.929 --> 09:23.929
<i> It's more competition</i>
<i> than I realized.</i>

09:24.031 --> 09:25.330
<i> This thing between us--</i>

09:25.399 --> 09:27.232
<i> it's new, tenuous.</i>

09:27.334 --> 09:29.701
<i> And the cost was a corpse.</i>

09:29.803 --> 09:31.803
<i> But I can't get rid of</i>
<i> every guy in New York.</i>

09:31.905 --> 09:34.539
<i> If I wanna win your heart,</i>
<i> I'm gonna have to show you--</i>

09:34.641 --> 09:37.409
[backboard thumping]
[Beck moaning]

09:37.511 --> 09:38.376
[creak, crack]

09:38.478 --> 09:39.878
- Aah!
[laughs]

09:39.980 --> 09:41.580
<i> - I'm not a "maybe."</i>

09:41.682 --> 09:43.148
<i> I'm</i> The One.

09:44.384 --> 09:48.086
<i> Time to get rid of Benji</i>

09:48.155 --> 09:50.589
<i> so I can focus</i>
<i> my undivided attention</i>

09:50.657 --> 09:53.191
<i> on you, Beck, on us.</i>

09:53.260 --> 09:55.193
<i> So I'm gonna need</i>
<i> a few supplies.</i>

09:55.295 --> 09:56.228
- Hey, Joe.

09:56.330 --> 09:58.463
You said
you needed to talk?

09:58.532 --> 10:00.365
- I do, yeah.
So here's the thing.

10:00.467 --> 10:02.334
I have a secret project
I'm working on,

10:02.436 --> 10:03.935
